item.title: Long Way to Run
item.description: Who was near me To get me over all the fear? Nice look (just look at you), sweet face (isn’t it sweet), But all the senses now gets me through as always, It’s not an ordinary me. And I don’t talk like everybody, It’s me: Myself for everyone. As long as you keep dream´ about me, Be the one, Come clean and say the words I’ve heard before. I know who was The one who let my senses free.
